<h1>Summary</h1>
<p>The geology based game I created is a platformer style game with a player who finds himself stuck near the center of
    the earth. The player must work his way to the surface while collecting coins, rocks, minerals, gemstones, and
    monster parts. The game is designed to be fun to play, but it also sprinkles some educational geology content
    throughout.</p>

