<h3>Design</h3>
<p>This game was designed using Unity 3D and programmed in C#. The graphics were designed by myself and a friend from
    high school. The designs were first drawn on paper and then converted into digital vectors using Illustrator CC.
    Then, the designs were rasterized into pixel art using Photoshop CC.</p>

